text.author: Ashley Claire
text.title: a college day in my life vlog // Ashley Claire
text.summary: Ash tells about her day, which includes a yoga class, marketing brand management class, doing some work while having coffee at Saxby's, and finally cooking pasta with peppers for dinner together with her boyfriend Harry.
